### Negustorii Cetatii (Catan-like) - Teste manuale
### Instaleaza extensia "REST Client" in VS Code (rangav.vscode-rest-client)

@host = http://localhost:8080
@idPartida = 2

### --- 0. Healthcheck ---
GET {{host}}/api/ping

### --- 1. Lista partide ---
GET {{host}}/api/partide

### --- 2. Creeaza o partida noua ---
POST {{host}}/api/partide
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nume": "Cetatea de test", "jucatoriMaxim": 3, "punctajCastig": 8 }

### --- 3. Adauga jucatori (modifica idPartida-ul de mai sus) ---
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/jucatori
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nume": "Vlad", "culoare": "albastru" }

###
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/jucatori
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nume": "Ion", "culoare": "rosu" }

### --- 4. Porneste partida (genereaza harta + intra in faza setup) ---
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/start

### --- 5. Vezi harta (hexagoane, varfuri, muchii) ---
GET {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/harta

### --- 6. Detalii partida (faza, jucator activ, etc.) ---
GET {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}

### --- SETUP (asezare initiala): trebuie un idVarf valid din harta ---
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/setup/asezare
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idVarf": 1 }

### Drumul initial - idMuchie adiacent asezarii
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/setup/drum
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idMuchie": 1 }

### --- JOC NORMAL ---

### 7. Arunca zarul
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari/zar

### 8. Construieste asezare (pe un varf liber, cu drum propriu adiacent)
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari/asezare
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idVarf": 5 }

### 9. Construieste drum
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari/drum
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idMuchie": 3 }

### 10. Upgrade asezare in cetate
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari/cetate
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idAsezare": 1 }

### 11. Paseaza tura
POST {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari/paseaza

### 12. Istoricul mutarilor
GET {{host}}/api/partide/{{idPartida}}/mutari

### --- Erori demo ---
GET {{host}}/api/partide/9999
GET {{host}}/api/partide/abc
